# Borussia Minerals — Cursor Rules

E-commerce site for museum-quality Arizona mineral specimens with interactive 3D Gaussian splat viewers.

**Repo:** github.com/idirectships/borussia-minerals (PUBLIC)
**Live:** borussiaminerals.com (Vercel)
**Owner:** Drew (Dru) Garman — GitHub: idirectships

---

## Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Framework | Next.js 16 (App Router) |
| Language | TypeScript 5.7 |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS 3.4 |
| Package Manager | Bun |
| 3D Viewer | `@mkkellogg/gaussian-splats-3d` v0.4.7 |
| Payments | Stripe (Checkout + Webhooks) |
| Inventory API | Google Sheets API v4 |
| File Storage | Vercel Blob (`.ksplat` splat files) |
| Deployment | Vercel (auto-deploy on push to master) |
| Testing | Playwright |
| Fonts | Cormorant Garamond (display) + Montserrat (body) |

**Node:** 20+ | **Build:** `bun dev`, `bun build`, `bun run lint`, `bun test`

---

## Project Structure

```
src/
