## Data Models

### Specimen
```typescript
interface Specimen {
  id: string                          // "azur-001", "cupr-001"
  name: string                        // "Azurite with Selenite"
  image: string                       // Hero photo path or Drive URL
  images?: string[]                   // Multi-image gallery (Drive URLs)
  locality: string                    // "Morenci Mine, Greenlee County, Arizona, USA"
  crystalSystem: string               // "Monoclinic", "Cubic"
  dimensions: string                  // "8.5 x 4.2 x 3.8 cm"
  weight?: string                     // "320g"
  description: string                 // Full narrative
  price?: number                      // USD cents (85000 = $850)
  availability: "available" | "sold" | "reserved"
  mineralGroup?: string               // "Carbonates", "Oxides"
  luster?: string                     // "Vitreous to adamantine"
  transparency?: string               // "Translucent to opaque"
  featured?: boolean                  // Homepage feature
  splatUrl?: string                   // Vercel Blob KSPLAT URL
  splatCamera?: { position: [number, number, number]; lookAt: [number, number, number] }
  hardness?: string                   // Mohs hardness
  sizeClass?: "TN" | "Min" | "SC" | "Cab"
  tier?: "museum" | "collector" | "select" | "classic"
  publishStatus?: "draft" | "review" | "published"
}
```

### Mine
```typescript
interface Mine {
  slug: string                        // "fat-jack"
  name: string                        // "Fat Jack Mine"
  location: string
  shortDescription: string
  history: string                     // Full narrative
  geology: string                     // Geological details
  heroImage?: string
  established?: string
  minerals?: string[]
}
```

### MineLocality (Map Pins)
```typescript
interface MineLocality {
  id: string                          // "morenci"
  name: string                        // "Morenci Mine"
  shortName: string                   // "Morenci"
  county: string                      // "Greenlee County"
  state: string                       // "Arizona"
  lat: number; lon: number
  description: string
  specimenIds: string[]
  minerals: string[]
}
```

### Current Localities (4)
1. Morenci Mine — Greenlee County (33.07, -109.37)
2. New Cornelia/Ajo — Pima County (32.37, -112.86)
3. Bagdad — Yavapai County (34.58, -113.15)
4. Ray/Pearl Handle Pit — Pinal County (33.15, -110.97)

